Resource Profile: Profile UICC TNM

Official URL: https://www.vision-zero-oncology.de/fhir/StructureDefinition/uicc-tnm Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2022-11-21 Computable Name: UICC_TNM

Copyright/Legal: CC-BY-SA-4.0

Profile for the tumor classification using TNM stage groups (I, II, III, or IV) and TNM staging elements (T, N, and M).

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile:
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Observation/example-tnm-TisN0M0, Observation/example-tnm-cT3pN0mol-sncM1, Observation/example-tnm-rpT3mpN0icM0R1is, Observation/example-tnm-uT2a2pN0023i-sncM1, Observation/example-tnm-ypT1bpN139snL0V0Pn1cM0R0
